        <definition>uint8_t cybt_controller_sleep_config_t::sleep_mode_enabled</definition>
        <argsstring></argsstring>
        <name>sleep_mode_enabled</name>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Enable or disable the sleep mode of BT chip. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Either assign the value CYBT_SLEEP_MODE_DISABLED, or CYBT_SLEEP_MODE_ENABLED</para>
<para>or CYCFG_BT_LP_ENABLED for ModusToolBox LPA configuration</para>
<para>Notice that sleep mode will be enabled only if both device and host wakeup pins are assigned. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
